                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/12742.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Saltillo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-04T20:00:00-06:41">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 4, 1914, 8 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Just as they were leaving, envoys requested me to have Department announce their
                    return to Mexico City.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
